---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Commercial Freedom in Mexico City | UTOPICA';
const description =
  'A commercial freedom model for Mexico City companies that unlocks decision-making, creativity, and responsiveness.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 space-y-10 text-gray-900">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-4xl">
        Commercial Freedom in Mexico City: A New Growth Model
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg">
      <p>
        In CDMX many companies operate with rigid structures that limit human potential. UTOPICA introduces a commercial freedom model that unlocks decision-making, creativity, and responsiveness.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Less control, more movement</h2>
        <p>
          Our methodology replaces excessive supervision with strategic autonomy, letting sales flow naturally.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Distributed responsibility</h2>
        <p>
          When decisions are distributed, speed increases and performance becomes emergent.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Continuous market adaptation</h2>
        <p>
          A flexible, light, adaptive model to compete successfully in the commercial ecosystem of CDMX.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>Want to unlock your organization’s commercial potential in Mexico City? Let’s talk.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="visibility:hidden;height:0;overflow:hidden;">
      commercial freedom CDMX, commercial autonomy CDMX, organic growth Mexico City, emergent performance CDMX, commercial movement, adaptive commercial structures, commercial transformation CDMX, flexible commercial model CDMX
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
